    <entry>
      <title>更新日志</title>
      <link href="/posts/gxrz.html"/>
      <url>/posts/gxrz.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.153(2022/10/24)</span><br><span class="line">1.删除黑名单、心跳等功能</span><br><span class="line">2.临时修复投票功能默认开启</span><br><span class="line">3.修复菜单命令异常</span><br><span class="line">4.新增40多接口指令</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">1.154(2022/10/25)</span><br><span class="line">1.优化头衔功能查询、添加、删除违禁词</span><br><span class="line">2.修复循环功能、空间功能开启异常</span><br><span class="line">3.优化抢包数据显示</span><br><span class="line">4.红包功能新增随机延迟回复格式与红包延迟一致</span><br><span class="line">5.修复部分功能导致的异常崩溃</span><br><span class="line">6.切换功能切换群友触发改为切换本群触发</span><br><span class="line">7.新增100多余接口指令</span><br><span class="line">8.修复接口功能异常</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.155（10.28）</span><br><span class="line">1.修复群发好友异常</span><br><span class="line">2.优化接口功能部分功能异常</span><br><span class="line">3.优化到期通知</span><br><span class="line">4.优化捡漏一笔画</span><br><span class="line">5.修复喷人功能自动关闭</span><br><span class="line">6.新增艾特功能、卡片、语音、随机回复(艾特功能自己艾特自己无效)</span><br><span class="line">7.修复主人功能拉黑、提黑后无法删除</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.156(2022/10/29)</span><br><span class="line">1.优化主人功能拉黑、提黑、踢黑写法</span><br><span class="line">2.修复撤回功能撤回链接</span><br><span class="line">3.优化撤回功能撤回上版本改动后导致的异常</span><br><span class="line">4.版本号  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.157(2022/10/31)</span><br><span class="line">1.新增签到功能签到失败艾特提示</span><br><span class="line">2.新增入群验证自动同意进群 (开启本功能无需验证直接同意进群)</span><br><span class="line">3.修复入群验证二次进群无法验证</span><br><span class="line">4.修复签到数据因目录变动导致凌晨刷新异常</span><br><span class="line">5.优化投票功能</span><br><span class="line">6.优化因模块导致的异常</span><br><span class="line">7.优化许可证退出异常</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.158(2022/11/3)</span><br><span class="line">1.修复好友图片功能、视频功能判断主人失败</span><br><span class="line">2.修复菜单两列显示不全、三列四列隐藏附页菜单</span><br><span class="line">3.更换JSon模块</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>QQ云端登录教程</title>
      <link href="/posts/b2760a56.html"/>
      <url>/posts/b2760a56.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>登录教程:<br>1.安卓下载TimQQ和爱加速(苹果不用下载TimQQ)<br>2.爱加速线路选择广州(不要清理爱加速后台挂着) TimQQ登录你的QQ<br>3.用TimQQ在群里发送申请登录<br>4.扫描二维码进行登录<br>密码登录教程:给机器人发送密码登录密码<br>比如密码登录123456<br>然后按照机器人给的操作进行操作即可</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">爱加速不能用了联系3109860881</span><br><span class="line">下面也算是一种扫码软件</span><br><span class="line">http://u3v.cn/6cIwFb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
  
  
    
    
